      "span_text": "The LixiLan-L trial  was a 30-week, double-blind trial, designed to confirm the superiority of IGlarLixi in comparison to glargine alone in patients with T2DM inadequately treated with a stable dose of insulin glargine and any other OAD. The mean starting A1c was 8.5%."
